    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I so agree with you! Growing up, my mom always cooked from scratch and made sure to have colorful meals.  She said that the variety of colors was how you could tell you were getting all your nutritional needs met.  She said and still says that a meal should never be all one color, especially beige.</p>
